description: Police in Belgium and France detain 13 people in an operation prompted by the deaths of 39 migrants.
title: Vietnamese migrant deaths in UK lorry spark 26 arrests
title_page: Vietnamese migrant deaths in UK lorry spark 26 arrests - BBC News
maintext: Among those who died was 26-year-old Pham Thi Tra My, who sent her family a message on 22 October saying she could not breathe and her "trip to a foreign land has failed".
